  "notes": "Rebuilds all Docker containers EXCEPT MySQL and N8N. Triggered via webhook or Slack dispatcher. Sequentially rebuilds Finance, HomeLab, Assistant, Sports, and Database APIs, waits 30s, health-checks all services, then reports success or failure to Slack.",
